<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dare-v">dare <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /deə(r)/    美 /der/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>[不用于进行时] 敢; 胆敢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try it if you dare.
有胆量你就试一试。</p></div>

<ul>
<li>dare to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Let your imagination run wild, and dare to dream.
放飞你的想象力，要敢于梦想。</p><footer>2013 广东</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>激将；激：</strong></h4>
<ul>
<li>dare sb to do sth: </li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They dared Tom to steal a bottle of his father’s whiskey.
他们激汤姆去偷爸爸的一瓶威士忌。</p></div></div>